{"tid":19453,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[高速打字]有冇人用過進化版速成","createTime":"2016-12-02T19:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T09:31:43.000Z","uid":21715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a119924aec81c03f6385e7f71eefcf36682391","tid":19453,"uid":21715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T19:18:18.000Z","msg":"之前上維基無意中見到<br />\n<br />\n快意速成:<a href=\"http://input.foruto.com/fast/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finput.foruto.com%2Ffast%2Findex.php&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=721fd4dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://input.foruto.com/fast/index.php</a><br />\n<br />\n佢唔同普通速成打兩碼之後要選字，選到眼都朦<br />\n<br />\n佢係打兩碼速成之後加多一碼廣東話拼音，例如要打&quot;我&quot;字，速成係打&quot;竹人&quot;，之後選字7。但快意速成就係打&quot;竹人N&quot;，之後直接出我字，免去選字眼矇嘅情況。姐係快意速成盲打唔洗背選字，就算係第一次打嘅字都可以盲打，令打字速度快好多。<br />\n<br />\n一開始係拉巴啲垃圾WIN7 32BIT 機用得好開心 真係好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n點知返到屋企安裝唔支援64BIT <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以係到推廣下，加上睇下有冇隱世高手可以再寫過個PROGRAM比64BIT 嘅SYSTEM 都用到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽講KAIBOARD嘅AUTHOR 都會上下LIHKG 希望你見到可以考慮下加佢入KAIBOARD啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:冇讀過IT"},{"pid":"cf440c7af5a95a8fa77c7a1124f5ec2be1e7b2b9","tid":19453,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T19:49:10.000Z","msg":"打慣左就唔使慢慢揀字啦<br />\n打得少就連頭兩個碼都錯 仲拼咩音"},{"pid":"a905f60016f7feb3dce253b770f0d9422d832bfd","tid":19453,"uid":50815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T20:01:40.000Z","msg":"打慣左都已經否以高速咁打字啦<br />\n拼音撚識咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2837f0cee5a78989f0c3d2ebcf1805a436bad